<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Redefinir Senha</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fffbea;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: auto;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      text-align: center;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #444;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #ffd633; /* amarelo suave */
      color: #222 !important;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #e6b800; /* amarelo mais forte no hover */
    }
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Redefinição de Senha</h1>
    <p>Olá {{.Name}},</p>
    <p>Clique no botão abaixo para abrir o aplicativo e redefinir sua senha no {{.AppName}}:</p>

    <a href="{{.DeepLink}}" class="button">Redefinir Senha</a>

    <p class="footer">Este link expira em 30 minutos.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
